title: BRIEF-Deltic Announces Preliminary Fourth Quarter 2017 Results
text:
Feb 14 (Reuters) - Deltic Timber Corp:
* DELTIC ANNOUNCES PRELIMINARY FOURTH QUARTER 2017 RESULTS * Q4 ADJUSTED EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.92 EXCLUDING ITEMS * Q4 EARNINGS PER SHARE $0.02 * Q4 SALES $72.1 MILLION VERSUS $58.5 MILLION * ‍REAL ESTATE SEGMENT OPERATING INCOME WAS LOWER IN Q4 OF 2017 COMPARED TO Q4 2016​
* ‍CURRENT YEAR PROVISION INCLUDED A $2.5 MILLION BENEFIT FROM REMEASUREMENT OF DEFERRED TAX LIABILITIES​
* ‍RESULTS FOR Q4 OF 2017 BENEFITED FROM INCREASED OPERATING INCOME IN WOODLANDS AND MANUFACTURING SEGMENTS​
* ‍DEMAND FOR COMPANY‘S TIMBER AND WOOD PRODUCTS “REMAINED STRONG” DURING Q4​ Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
